                            Lister of the Minerals Section, Division of International
                        Resources, to the Chief of the Division (
                        Lipkowitz
                    )</title></titleStmt><sourceDesc><bibl type="frus-volume-id">frus1946v11</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-id">d549</bibl><bibl type="frus-document-number">549</bibl><bibl type="frus-div-subtype">historical-document</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><settingDesc><setting><date notBefore="1946-09-10T00:00:00-05:00" notAfter="1946-09-10T23:59:59-05:00"/></setting></settingDesc></profileDesc></teiHeader><text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-09-10T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-09-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="549" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d549">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">825.51/9–1046</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Memorandum by Mr. <persName type="from">Louis
                            Lister</persName> of the Minerals Section, Division of International
                        Resources, to the Chief of the Division</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Lipkowitz</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1946-09-10">September 10,
                            1946</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Stenger,<note n="94" xml:id="d549fn1">Jerome J. Stenger, Special Assistant,
                        Division of Investment and Economic Development.</note>
                    <gloss target="#t_ED1">ED</gloss>, has given me the following information
                    regarding Chile’s request for an <gloss target="#t_Eximbank1">Eximbank</gloss>
                    loan. The request is for a $40,000,000 loan, half of which is to be allocated to
                    the Fomento Corp. and the other half to the Chilean State Railways. The funds
                    are allocated to the following groups of industries: <table cols="4" rows="15">
                        <row>
                            <cell>
                                <hi rend="italic">Fomento Corp</hi>.</cell>
                            <cell>
                                <hi rend="italic">Millions of Dollars</hi>
                            </cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Hydroelectric</cell>
                            <cell role="num">5.5</cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Petroleum Explorations</cell>
                            <cell role="num">5.0</cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Agricultural Machinery Plants</cell>
                            <cell role="num">3.2</cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Wood &amp; Lumber Projects</cell>
                            <cell role="num">3.4</cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Transportation</cell>
                            <cell role="num">3.6</cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Copper Manufacturers</cell>
                            <cell role="num">0.6</cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Cement Manufactures</cell>
                            <cell role="num">0.5</cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Fish Industry</cell>
                            <cell rendition="#underline" role="num">0.5</cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell rend="padding-left: 3em">Total</cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell role="num">22.3</cell>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>
                                <hi rend="italic">Chilean State Railways</hi>
                            </cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Rolling Stock</cell>
                            <cell role="num">5.00</cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Electrification</cell>
                            <cell rendition="#underline" role="num">16.25</cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell rend="padding-left: 3em">Total</cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell rendition="#underline" role="num">21.25</cell>
                            <cell/>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell rend="padding-left: 4em">
                                <hi rend="italic">Grand Total</hi>
                            </cell>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell/>
                            <cell rendition="#underline" role="num">43.55<note n="*" xml:id="d549fn2">Loan requested is for $40,000,000 [Footnote in
                                    the original.]</note>
                            </cell>
                        </row>
                    </table>
                </p>
                <p>The request is currently before the <gloss target="#t_NAC1">NAC</gloss>, which,
                    according to Mr. Stenger, has not yet taken any action.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
</TEI>
